{
  "name": "bench-app-vike",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "private": true,
  "description": "Benchmark baseline: a Vike + React (SSR) Notes app composed from the vike-* extension family (vike-auth owns identity + sessions, the universal ORM owns notes, vike-ai owns summarize). Twin of bench-app-next. Phase 1 of #330.",
